		{"id":"b1a2c3d4e5f60002","type":"text","text":"## 👤 PM / TPM\nNatural language input via **OpenCode TUI**\n`/command` or free-form prompt","x":380,"y":-415,"width":500,"height":110},
		{"id":"b1a2c3d4e5f60041","type":"text","text":"### SKILL.md → Context Injection\n**5 Agent Skills:**\n`obsidian-cli` · `obsidian-markdown`\n`obsidian-bases` · `json-canvas` · `defuddle`\n\nInjected as LLM context.\nLLM executes CLI commands directly.","x":-440,"y":700,"width":520,"height":140},
		{"id":"b1a2c3d4e5f60022","type":"text","text":"### Atlassian Rovo MCP\n**Official**: atlassian-mcp-server\nCloud-hosted: `mcp.atlassian.com`\nJira + Confluence + Compass\nOAuth 2.1 / API token","x":1320,"y":730,"width":280,"height":140},
		{"id":"b1a2c3d4e5f60023","type":"text","text":"### BigQuery MCP\n**Data warehouse queries**\nExecute SQL · Dataset/table info\nData insights & forecasts","x":1640,"y":730,"width":280,"height":140},
		{"id":"b1a2c3d4e5f60011","type":"text","text":"### Custom Commands\n`.opencode/commands/*.md`\nSkill modules:\n`/hello-boyo`\n`/requirements-analysis`\n`/enrich-document`\n`/system-explainer`","x":40,"y":210,"width":340,"height":170},
		{"id":"b1a2c3d4e5f60012","type":"text","text":"### ⭐ LLM Engine\n**Gemini** (Vertex AI) — primary\n**Claude** — fallback\n\nAgentic reasoning & orchestration.\nThe brain that drives everything.","x":440,"y":210,"width":380,"height":170,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b1a2c3d4e5f60013","type":"text","text":"### MCP Client\nBuilt into OpenCode.\nRoutes tool calls from LLM → MCP Servers.\nProtocol-based integration.","x":880,"y":210,"width":380,"height":170},
		{"id":"b1a2c3d4e5f60032","type":"text","text":"### Confluence / Jira\n**Company knowledge & project tracking**\nRequirements, specs, epics, issues","x":1230,"y":1475,"width":370,"height":140},
		{"id":"b1a2c3d4e5f60033","type":"text","text":"### BigQuery Tables\n**Data warehouse**\nMetrics, analytics, business data","x":1640,"y":1475,"width":370,"height":140},
		{"id":"b1a2c3d4e5f60031","type":"text","text":"### ⭐ Obsidian Vault\n**Local knowledge graph**\nDocuments as graph nodes:\nfrontmatter + `[[wikilinks]]`\nPrimary knowledge source","x":430,"y":1475,"width":380,"height":140},
		{"id":"b1a2c3d4e5f60034","type":"text","text":"### Local Repo Clones\n**Service codebases** (~/repos/)\nLocal git clones of key services.\nAgent reads code on TPM's behalf.\nRefreshed via `git pull`.","x":30,"y":1475,"width":370,"height":140},
		{"id":"b1a2c3d4e5f60060","type":"text","text":"### 🌐 Obsidian Web Clipper\n**Browser extension** — 一键 clip\nCustom templates for:\nConfluence · Jira · Articles · Meetings\nAI Interpreter: auto-summary + tags\nClips land in `00-Inbox/`","x":980,"y":-415,"width":480,"height":110}
	],
